comments.body:
After a lot of debugging headache, finally have a patch that works. Its still undergoing some testing. 
@Alejandro, I used part of the patch you uploaded since it was a bit cleaner than what I had. Thanks for that :). 

This uses a facade for Counter and Group in mapred.Counters. This leads to a string of issues related to serialization which I have fixed by exposing the real objects in the facade.
